    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/j0rgbv-09/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_PRODUCT&editorId=604270697505620651&sectionId=604271108329308843)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWddcJAESW_text","label":"ggWddcJAESW_text","default":"<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Do You Still Have Any Doubts?</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_0","label":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_0","default":"<p>What happened to Omnis? Why is it now SerlinoLab?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_1","label":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_1","default":"<p>Can it be found in stores/pharmacies?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_2","label":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_2","default":"<p>How long does it take to see results?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_3","label":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_3","default":"<p>How to use it?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_4","label":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_4","default":"<p>How does the 60-day guarantee work?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_5","label":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_5","default":"<p>How long does this cream last?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_6","label":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_6","default":"<p>Is it suitable for sensitive skin?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_7","label":"ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_7","default":"<p>What ingredients are in the eye contour?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeyv3nvcwe_text","label":"ggeyv3nvcwe_text","default":"<p>We updated our name and packaging to better reflect the true Italian identity of our brand.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The formulas? Exactly the same.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Same ingredients, same quality, same lab on the Amalfi Coast.</p><p>Just a new look.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We hope you like it as much as we do</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4E8myjkrY_text","label":"gg4E8myjkrY_text","default":"<p><strong>NO </strong>at the moment the <strong>SerlinoLab Eye Contour is only available on our website.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We have chosen to sell only online to <strong>maintain competitive prices</strong> by avoiding intermediaries and <strong>offer </strong>a shopping experience with <strong>personalized advice</strong> for each customer on WhatsApp, which would not be possible in physical stores.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggR0ua9eMRk_text","label":"ggR0ua9eMRk_text","default":"<p>Like any investment, give this product the benefit of time. The best results are achieved with continued use, twice a day, for 8-12 weeks.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwnWc2z9ft_text","label":"ggwnWc2z9ft_text","default":"<p><strong>Morning and evening,</strong> after cleaning and drying your face, press the button located on the top of the bottle once and distribute the cream around the eye contour.<br><br>Using the metal ball massager, <strong>make circular movements until completely absorbed.</strong><br><br>A single dose is enough for both eyes.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7xPh9jIxj_text","label":"gg7xPh9jIxj_text","default":"<p>If after 60 days you haven't seen the results you expected, you can write to us and you will be <strong>refunded 100%</strong>... yes we are that confident in our products!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUqzxYOX9P_text","label":"ggUqzxYOX9P_text","default":"<p>With daily use morning and evening, the cream will last you for 1 month.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLeXHdEWgH_text","label":"ggLeXHdEWgH_text","default":"<p>The SerlinoLab eye contour is made with the highest quality ingredients. Suitable for every skin type, even the most sensitive ones. Particularly recommended for mature skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnj2HWJKbX_text","label":"ggnj2HWJKbX_text","default":"<p>The main ingredients are hyaluronic acid, caffeine and acetyl hexapeptide-8.<br><br>You can find the complete list here:<br><br>INCI<br><br>Aqua, aloe barbadensis leaf juice, glycerin, sodium polyacrylate, niacinamide, oryza sativa bran oil, phenoxyethanol, caffeine, tocopheryl acetate, helianthus annuus seed oil, urea, trehalose, hydrolyzed rice protein, ethylhexylglycerin, citrus aurantium bergamia fruit oil, sodium carboxymethyl betaglucan, lavandula angustifolia oil, linalool, limonene, sodium benzoate, linalyl acetate, althaea officinalis root extract, calendula officinalis flower extract, malva sylvestris leaf extract, hydroxyethylcellulose, potassium sorbate, sodium hyaluronate, benzyl alcohol, caprylyl glycol, pinene, acetyl hexapeptide-8, ascorbic acid, citric acid, pentapeptide-18.</p>"}],
